<text><body>
<lb n="0507b07"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0507b08"/>
<lb n="0507b09"/><head type="no">No. 116 [Nos. 99(1073), 100(12), 117,
<lb n="0507b10"/>125(23.5)]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0507b11"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><title>佛說戒德香經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0507b12"/>
<lb n="0507b13"/><byline type="Translator">東晉天竺三藏竺曇無蘭譯</byline>
<lb n="0507b14"/><p>聞如是。一時佛遊舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。時
<lb n="0507b15"/>賢者阿難閑居獨思。世有三香。一曰根香。
<lb n="0507b16"/>二曰枝香。三曰華香。是三品香唯隨風香不
<lb n="0507b17"/>能逆風。寧有雅香隨風逆風者乎。賢者阿難
<lb n="0507b18"/>獨處思惟於義所歸不知所趣。即從坐起往
<lb n="0507b19"/>詣佛所。稽首<note n="0507008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔佛〕－【三】</note><note n="0507008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔佛〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507008"><lem>佛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>足下<note n="0507009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔長跪叉手〕－【三】</note><note n="0507009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔長跪叉手〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507009"><lem>長跪叉手</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0507010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">而＝前【三】</note><note n="0507010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">而＝前【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507010"><lem>而</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">前</rdg></app>白佛言。
<lb n="0507b20"/>我獨處思惟。世有三香。一曰根香。二曰枝香。
<lb n="0507b21"/>三曰華香。此三品香唯能隨風不能逆風。寧
<lb n="0507b22"/>有雅香隨風逆風者乎。佛告阿難。善哉善哉。
<lb n="0507b23"/>誠如汝問。有香真正隨風逆風。阿難白佛。願
<lb n="0507b24"/>聞其<note n="0507011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">香＝意【三】</note><note n="0507011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">香＝意【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507011"><lem>香</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>佛言。若於郡國縣邑村落。有善男
<lb n="0507b25"/>子善女人。修行十善身不殺盜<note n="0507012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">淫＝婬【三】</note><note n="0507012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">淫＝婬【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507012"><lem>淫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婬</rdg></app>。口不妄
<lb n="0507b26"/>言兩舌惡口綺語。意不嫉<note n="0507013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔&CB00107;〕－【三】</note><note n="0507013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔&CB00107;〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507013"><lem>&CB00107;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>恚癡。孝順父
<lb n="0507b27"/>母奉事<note n="0507014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三尊＝三寶【三】</note><note n="0507014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">三尊＝三寶【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507014"><lem>三尊</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">三寶</rdg></app>。仁慈道德威儀禮節。東方無數
<lb n="0507b28"/>沙門梵志歌頌其德。南西北方四維上下沙
<lb n="0507b29"/>門梵志咸歌其德。某郡國土縣邑村落。有善
<pb ed="T" id="T02.0116.0507c" n="0507c"/>
<lb n="0507c01"/>男子善女人。<note n="0507015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">奉行十＝及奉行【三】</note><note n="0507015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">奉行十＝及奉行【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507015"><lem>奉行十</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">及奉行</rdg></app>善敬事三寶。孝順仁慈
<lb n="0507c02"/>道德恩義不失禮節。是香名曰隨風逆風靡
<lb n="0507c03"/>不周。照十方宣德一切蒙賴。佛時頌曰。</p>
<lb n="0507c04"/><lg><l>雖有美香花</l><l>不能逆風熏</l>
<lb n="0507c05"/><l>不息名栴檀</l><l>眾雨一切香</l>
<lb n="0507c06"/><l>志性能和雅</l><l>爾乃逆風香</l>
<lb n="0507c07"/><l>正士名丈夫</l><l>普熏于十方</l>
<lb n="0507c08"/><l>木<note n="0507016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蜜＝&CB00189;【元】【明】</note><app n="0507016"><lem>蜜</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&CB00189;</rdg></app>及栴檀</l><l>青蓮諸雨香</l>
<lb n="0507c09"/><l>一切此眾香</l><l>戒香最無上</l>
<lb n="0507c10"/><l>是等清淨<note n="0507017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">者＝戒【三】</note><note n="0507017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">者＝戒【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507017"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">戒</rdg></app></l><l>所行無放逸</l>
<lb n="0507c11"/><l>不知魔徑路</l><l>不見所歸趣</l>
<lb n="0507c12"/><l>此道至永安</l><l>此道最無上</l>
<lb n="0507c13"/><l>所獲斷穢源</l><l>降伏絕魔網</l>
<lb n="0507c14"/><l>用上佛道堂</l><l>昇無窮之慧</l>
<lb n="0507c15"/><l>以此宣<note n="0507018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＝維【三】</note><note n="0507018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">經＝維【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507018"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">維</rdg></app>義</l><l>除去一切弊</l></lg>
<lb n="0507c16"/><p>佛告阿難。是香所布<note n="0507019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">不＝無【三】</note><note n="0507019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">不＝無【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507019"><lem>不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app>礙須彌山川天地。不
<lb n="0507c17"/>礙四種地水火風。通達八極上下亦然。無窮
<lb n="0507c18"/>之界咸歌其德。一身不殺<note n="0507020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝盜媱【三】</note><note n="0507020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝盜媱【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507020"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">盜媱</rdg></app>。世世長壽。其
<lb n="0507c19"/>命無<note n="0507021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">橫＝限【三】</note><note n="0507021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">橫＝限【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507021"><lem>橫</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">限</rdg></app>。不盜竊者。世世富饒又不<note n="0507022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">妄＝忘【三】</note><note n="0507022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">妄＝忘【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507022"><lem>妄</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">忘</rdg></app>遺財
<lb n="0507c20"/>寶。常存施為道根。不<note n="0507023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬色者＝婬失者【三】</note><note n="0507023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬色者＝婬失者【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507023"><lem>婬色者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">婬失者</rdg></app>。<note n="0507024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【三】</note><note n="0507024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔人〕－【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507024"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不犯<note n="0507025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（他）＋妻【三】</note><note n="0507025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（他）＋妻【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507025"><lem>妻</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">他妻</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0507c21"/>所在化生蓮華之中。不妄言者。口氣香好言
<lb n="0507c22"/><note n="0507026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輒＝可【三】</note><note n="0507026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">輒＝可【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507026"><lem>輒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">可</rdg></app>信之。不兩舌者。家常和合無<note n="0507027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有別離＝別離業【三】</note><note n="0507027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有別離＝別離業【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507027"><lem>有別離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">別離業</rdg></app>。不
<lb n="0507c23"/>惡口者。其舌常好言辭辯通。不綺<note n="0507028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝言【三】</note><note n="0507028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">語＝言【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507028"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">言</rdg></app>者。人
<lb n="0507c24"/>聞其言莫不諮受宣用為珍。不嫉&CB00107;者。世世
<lb n="0507c25"/>所生眾人所敬。不瞋恚者。世世端正人見歡
<lb n="0507c26"/><note n="0507029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喜＝然【三】</note><note n="0507029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">喜＝然【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0507029"><lem>喜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">然</rdg></app>。除愚癡者。所生智慧靡不諮請。捨于邪
<lb n="0507c27"/>見常住正道。從行所得各自然生。故當棄邪
<lb n="0507c28"/>從其真妙。佛說如是。時諸比丘聞之歡喜。作
<lb n="0507c29"/>禮而去。</p>
